685a8d2c21f9dc580","tid":2174253,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f401398521bfc3f3f9e1e339b8c68e6b0f123f8","tid":2174253,"uid":347695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d901be9476d109b4572f734cc730fe5da0f42e76","tid":2174253,"uid":159818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"不嬲3成黃3成藍4成港豬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T19:22:04.000Z","msg":"而家啲藍絲愈吹愈大<br />\n多左好多文宣/論文<br />\n附和嘅人好似多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T22:50:34.000Z","msg":"都係果班人者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前區議會藍屍就多人多資源  <br />\n<br />\n普通人一出聲又拉又投訴  <br />\n<br />\n雙重標準  普通人唔出得聲者<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為藍屍好多人"},{"pid":"2645f5cfe84a396135d34eb759c6463d1790e151","tid":2174253,"uid":69294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d901be9476d109b4572f734cc730fe5da0f42e76","tid":2174253,"uid":159818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"不嬲3成黃3成藍4成港豬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:03:13.000Z","msg":"6成黃 4成藍左右啦<br />\n但黃入面都有30%-40%係港豬心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c34a648ea0f069185e64804f900144abfb86bb","tid":2174253,"uid":189465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:09:22.000Z","msg":"香港自所謂「回歸」到現在足足廿三年<br />\n經歷過大大小小嘅風雨<br />\n到現在 黃藍之比亦只係六四比<br />\n<br />\n搞笑嘅係 唔少香港人仍然會笑其他地方嘅人多藍<br />\n例如：澳門 馬來西亞 新加坡等等<br />\n明明連自己香港嘅藍都仲有約40%<br />\n都仲夠膽走出去笑人哋「未覺醒」「抵死」<br />\n與其笑人 不如諗下點將黃營嘅比例推高罷啦"},{"pid":"9190f34e7fb4976b86bad5a1d4c8fbf21cb67c92","tid":2174253,"uid":347695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2645f5cfe84a396135d34eb759c6463d1790e151","tid":2174253,"uid":69294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d901be9476d109b4572f